## Severity Levels

### Warning (Recommended Fix)
- PascalCase in camelCase files
- kebab-case in camelCase files
- Missing standard suffixes

### Error (Must Fix)
- UPPERCASE file names
- Special characters in names
- Inconsistent extensions

## Integration

### Pre-commit Hook
```bash
#!/bin/sh
npm run cursor-rules-check
if [ $? -ne 0 ]; then
  echo "File naming convention violations detected"
  exit 1
fi
```

### CI/CD Pipeline
```yaml
- name: Check File Naming Conventions
  run: npm run cursor-rules-check
```

